#4852
Name Four Morningstars~
Desc This shop appears to sell forged crafts. It is rather utilitarian in 
construction, having just a few sturdy wooden racks for display items, and a 
long pine counter in the center of the shop. Four smouldering sconces are 
mounted here, one in each corner of the room, providing just enough light to 
see. There is a smell of blood in the air as well, but none can be seen. The 
only other decoration in the shop is a large banner hanging across the back 
wall. 
~
RoomFlags indoors light~
Room2Flags player_shop~
Sector inside~
RoomEcho  0 23   5 A rat scurries across the floor.~
ExtraDesc banner ~
This rough banner shows an image of a burning palm tree on a black 
background. It appears to be made of burlap. 
~
ExtraDesc sconce ~
This is nothing more than an oil-filled goblet fastened to the wall. It has 
been set aflame and is smoking profusely. 
~
ExtraDesc wooden rack~
These racks look as though they have been crafted solely for holding weapons 
and armor for display. They are very roughly made. 
~
ExtraDesc long pine counter~
This sturdy counter stands about three and a half feet tall and is 
unfinished. Carefull touching it unless you enjoy splinters. The top surface 
looks a bit worn-in. 
~
