#4858
Name Arcane Emporium~
Desc A stylish market for academic research and studies. The left wall is 
brimming with tomes, books and scrolls. The right panel  is covered in 
scrolls, organized in a savvy method for clients to peruse. Academic 
professionals and folks simply in need of a potion are greeted by a 
gracious, perky elven teenage girl who is also a  magi apprentice, that 
works here to study and earn wages. The colors are spiffy and comfortable, 
magenta and white tones give the shop a serenity and yet cordial reflection. 
Behind the oak counter, she has a classy desk to sit at while awaiting for 
customers. There are many plants, wind-chimes , incense and various candles 
gives the room a mystical and receptive ambiance when one surveys their 
surroundings. 
